[
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103_0",
    "text": "4.西南地区地质灾害严重",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.10599721059972106,
      0.1673254281949934,
      0.3719200371920037,
      0.18906455862977603
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103",
    "order": 1
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103_1",
    "text": "形成原因：",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.13575081357508137,
      0.19894598155467721,
      0.25290562529056254,
      0.22002635046113306
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103",
    "order": 2
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103_2",
    "text": "(1) 自然原因：山区面积广大.岩石破碎.风化严重；干湿季分明、暴雨集中：地 壳运动强烈山体中断层发育。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.10320781032078104,
      0.22924901185770752,
      0.9344490934449093,
      0.2839262187088274
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103_3",
    "text": "(2)人为原因：对植被的破坏 治理措施：恢复植被",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.13482101348210135,
      0.29117259552042163,
      0.4583914458391446,
      0.3458498023715415
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103_4",
    "text": "三农业区位分析",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.10692701069270107,
      0.38735177865612647,
      0.2807996280799628,
      0.4077733860342556
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103_5",
    "text": "1.灌溉农业区位分析",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.12273361227336123,
      0.41699604743083,
      0.34774523477452346,
      0.43873517786561267
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103_6",
    "text": "典型地区：宁夏平原.河套平原.河西走廊、南疆等",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1413296141329614,
      0.4479578392621871,
      0.6276150627615062,
      0.47101449275362317
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103",
    "order": 7
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103_7",
    "text": "分析自然区位因素：热量充足，温差大：地形平坦：土壤肥沃：灌溉水源充足 不足：水资源短缺：冬季受寒潮和暴风雪影响；土壤的盐碱化等",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1413296141329614,
      0.47891963109354413,
      0.8637842863784286,
      0.5322793148880105
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103",
    "order": 8
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103_8",
    "text": "2.商品谷物农业 典型地区：东北地区 分析区位因素",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.11715481171548117,
      0.5731225296442688,
      0.3412366341236634,
      0.6574440052700923
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103",
    "order": 9
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103_9",
    "text": "(1)自然因素：温带季风气候，夏季高温多雨，雨热同期：地形平坦开阁：耕地面积 广大：土壤肥沃：水源充足。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.09576940957694095,
      0.6666666666666666,
      0.9186424918642492,
      0.7206851119894598
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103",
    "order": 10
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103_10",
    "text": "(2)社会经济因素：地广人稀，农产品商品率高；生产规模大.机械化水平高：交通 便利：市场广阔：工业比较发达：国家政策支持。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.09576940957694095,
      0.7285902503293807,
      0.9139934913993492,
      0.7839262187088274
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103",
    "order": 11
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103_11",
    "text": "不足：热量不足：土地沙化、水工流失加剧：土壤肥力下降：冬季受寒潮和冻害的 影响等。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.09483960948396095,
      0.7905138339920948,
      0.9121338912133892,
      0.8438735177865613
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103",
    "order": 12
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103_12",
    "text": "与美国商品谷物农业比较：",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1506276150627615,
      0.8544137022397892,
      0.41562064156206413,
      0.8761528326745718
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103",
    "order": 13
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103_13",
    "text": "相同点：农业地域类型相同：地广人稀，农产品商品率高：生产规模大，机械化水",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.1515574151557415,
      0.8847167325428195,
      0.9084146908414691,
      0.9084321475625824
    ],
    "page": "notes_1ba14cb325bc448f7201b20502ecf2b5_103",
    "order": 14
  }
]